PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING THE NATIONAL PARKS WILDLIFE REGULATIONS which revise the definition of "wildlife" to include all wild animals, insects, fish and invertebrates, make it an offence to traffic in or remove wildlife from a National Park, and extend the ban on firearms to Forillon National Park.

precis:
REGULATIONS AMENDING THE NATIONAL PARKS WILDLIFE REGULATIONS which revise
the definition of "wildlife" to include all wild animals, insects, fish and
invertebrates, make it an offence to traffic in or remove wildlife from a
National Park, and extend the ban on firearms to Forillon National Park.
